OL,3,CMore than two overdoses per day in
OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FEvery day, of every month, for the
OL,8,Fpast three years, an ambulance has
OL,9,Fbeen dispatched somewhere in largely
OL,10,Frural southern Scotland to deal with a
OL,11,Fsuspected overdose.
OL,13,FExclusive data obtained by ITV News
OL,14,FBorder showed that there were an
OL,15,Faverage of 2.2 ambulance call-outs to
OL,16,Fa suspected overdose across Dumfries
OL,17,Fand Galloway and the Scottish Borders
OL,18,Fin 2023, with a total of 821 recorded
OL,19,Fduring the year.
