OL,3,CMore than two overdoses per day in
OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FHowever figures have dropped slightly
OL,8,Fsince 2021, when the data showed an
OL,9,Faverage of 2.4 incidents a day were
OL,10,Frecorded.
OL,12,FData was obtained via a Freedom of
OL,13,FInformation request to the Scottish
OL,14,FAmbulance Service, and isn't broken
OL,15,Fdown by type of overdose - so could
OL,16,Finclude those caused by alcohol and
OL,17,Fother legal substances. It also
OL,18,Fdoesn't differentiate between
OL,19,Fdeliberate and accidental overdoses.
