OL,7,FScott Richardson, a harm reduction
OL,8,Fworker for the drug and alcohol
OL,9,Fcharity With You in the border's town
OL,10,Fof Galashiels, said he wasn't
OL,11,Fsurprised by the numbers.
OL,13,F"There is a lot of people out there
OL,14,Fwho are having some challenges with
OL,15,Fsubstance misuse at the moment," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
