OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FHe suggested that poly-drug use, where
OL,8,Fpeople use more than one substance at
OL,9,Fthe same time, was contributing to the
OL,10,Fnumbers. There are also concerns that
OL,11,Fpowerful nitazene type drugs are
OL,12,Fentering the supply, increasing the
OL,13,Frisks of overdose.
OL,15,F"It's the strength, the potency of
OL,16,Fit," Scott explained. "It's a lot more
OL,17,Fstronger than heroin."
