OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FScotland remains the drug deaths
OL,8,Fcapital of Europe, recording 1,172
OL,9,Fdeaths in 2023. One former addict who
OL,10,Fnow volunteers for support service
OL,11,FBorders in Recovery told ITV News he
OL,12,Fhad suffered from multiple overdoses.
OL,14,F"My go to substances were the ones
OL,15,Fthat numbed me the most," Scott Happer
OL,16,Fsaid. "Heroin, benzodiazepines, which,
OL,17,Ftaken together, can be really
OL,18,Fdangerous."
OL,20,F"I'm lucky to be here really," he
OL,21,Fadded.
