OL,3,CMore than two overdoses per day in
OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FScott credits a treatment called
OL,8,FNaloxone for saving his life. Produced
OL,9,Fas both an injection and a nasal
OL,10,Fspray, it rapidly reverses the affects
OL,11,Fof an opioid overdose. The Scottish
OL,12,FGovernment launched a national scheme
OL,13,Frolling it out across the country in
OL,14,F2011, and say they continue to
OL,15,Fencourage health boards to embed it
OL,16,Fwithin local areas.
