OL,4,Csouth of Scotland - with figures
OL,5,Cclimbing
OL,7,FIn a statement the Scottish Health
OL,8,FSecretary Neil Gray said: "Increasing
OL,9,Fthe provision and availability of
OL,10,Fnaloxone, which provides time for
OL,11,Femergency services to arrive and for
OL,12,Ffurther treatment to be given, is a
OL,13,Fkey priority in our national mission
OL,14,Fto reduce harm and help save lives.
OL,16,F"Figures show 7,589 take home naloxone
OL,17,Fkits were issued from October to
OL,18,FDecember last year for those at risk
OL,19,Fof opioid overdose.
